16. Docker Compose (Multi-Container Applications — SRE Perspective)

Most real systems include multiple services.

Application
Database
Cache
Message queue

Docker Compose allows running distributed systems locally.

Example docker-compose.yml

version: "3.9"

services:
app:
image: nginx
container_name: sre-app
ports:
- "8080:80"
depends_on:
- redis
restart: always

redis:
image: redis:7
volumes:
- redis_data:/data

volumes:
redis_data:

Run the environment

docker compose up -d
docker compose ps
docker compose logs
docker compose down

Compose prepares engineers for Kubernetes concepts.

Service → Pod
Network → Cluster networking
Volumes → Persistent Volumes

